user.biography: You can get to tap lists, tasting room info, to-go ordering, coffee, merch, the blog, & special release presales by following this link:

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 19, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
PRESALE BEER: DDH Finally Open in Anaheim. Leisuretown is coming up on its one-year anniversary (what?!), and we’re celebrating by doubling down on the DIPA that celebrated its grand opening. Hopped with Mosaic, Citra, Strata, and Idaho-7, this 8% birthday party in a can will lavish your taste buds with a dazzling array of fruity, dank, and tropical notes.
—
You'll be able to secure your allotment in Saturday's online presale. All the details will go out via our email newsletter, which you can sign up for at moderntimesbeer.com.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 18, 2021. May be an image of drink and outdoors.

node.text: We love Brain Vacation, and we don't care who knows it. This enchantingly spritzy tropical gose is loaded with pineapple, passion fruit, guava, and orange, making for an unparalleled 3.3% beverage experience. If you haven't made it official yet, you can snag a 6-er at our spots, as well as at fine beverage retailers throughout our regular realms of distribution.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 17, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Whatever your plans are today--whether you're in for a good-old-fashioned float  or mowing the lawn--you can totally snag cans of this insanely delicious West Coast-style IPA at our spots. It's virtually guaranteed to serve you well, wherever your day takes you.

PACKAGING TEAM APPRECIATION! These tireless, multitasking super-humans run 2 super delicate machines, ripping through 200 barrels (at least) per day. That means packing up thousands of cases so that beer can be delivered to all your faces, fresh. We are eternally grateful for this hardworking bunch, and if you've ever enjoyed cracking an MT can, you should be too.
--
From our Packaging Manager: 
Where do we even begin with this team... These folks are the are one of the main reasons we are still operating as a company; knocking out pack plans and packaging day and night to meet orders and trucking needs. This team has overcome tremendous odds and maintained a 200+ bbl average throughout the entire pandemic shutdown, while adhering to strict quality & food safety guidelines. But that's not all...They learned a brand new case packer machine--top to bottom--and also kept up with our raw material warehousing (40 pallets on average per week). To say these folks are superheroes is an understatement. Cheers to you all, Packaging Team.

Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'CELEBRATING THE LIFE OF sho JULY 31ST. 1PM-4PM 3612 KURTZ Nasho ST SAN DIEGO TICKETS ON SALE NOW TICKET PRICE: $20 TICKETS INCLUDE 8 4oz POURS & MEMORIAL TASTER GLASS'.

node.text:
TICKETS ARE ON SALE! If you'd like to join us in Celebrating the Life of Nate Soroko on 7/31, you are totally welcome to. We'll be pouring some excellent beverages alongside a bunch of decidedly tight guest breweries while we cheers to a singularly wonderful human being. Your $20 ticket gets you a memorial taster glass, with which you can get 8 4oz pours. Friends and family will gather from 1PM-4PM at our San Diego barrel warehouse, the Fortress of Raditude. Tickets can be found in our online store, or by following the profile link.
--
This event will benefit a local non-profit that provides culinary apprenticeships to people in need of a career and a fresh start.

node.text: ANNIVERSARY RADNESS! This weekend, MT8! (8% DIPA with Riwaka, Nelson, & Mosaic hops, & Sauvignon Blanc grape dust) is hitting all tasting rooms as an extra special birthday treat. We'll also be pouring Mega Devil's Teeth with Coconut, Cocoa, Maple, & Almonds, plus a few other tasty little surprises. We'd love it if you swung by our spots for a toast.

node.text:
CELEBRATING THE LIFE OF NATE SOROKO! On 7/31 from 1PM-4PM, friends, family, and a bunch of rad guest breweries will congregate at the Fortress of Raditude to remember an extraordinary person and enjoy a few extremely choice beverages.
—
Tickets will go on sale FRIDAY AT 10AM via our online store. Your $30 ticket grants you access and a memorial taster glass, with which you can get 8 tasty 4oz pours. 
—
GUEST BREWERIES
•	Sante Adairius Rustic Ales
•	Almanac Beer Co.
•	California Wild Ales
•	Casa Agria Specialty Ales
•	Cellarmaker Brewing Co.
•	Fall Brewing Co. 
•	Fieldwork Brewing Co.
•	Firestone Walker Brewing Co.
•	Green Cheek Beer Co.
•	Moksa Brewing Co.
•	North Park Beer Co.
•	Pizza Port Brewing Co.
•	Russian River Brewing Co.
•	Societe Brewing Co.
•	More TBA
—
This event will benefit a local San Diego non-profit that offers culinary apprenticeships to people in need of a career and a fresh start.

node.text: HEADS-UP, CALIFORNIA: You can totally get the Ultimate 6-Pack Mixed Pack delivered right to your door. We've somewhat recently forayed into the realm of 12 oz-ers, so we've made easy to get a sampling with this case of killer beers: Abaddon (Helles lager), Brain Vacation (spritzy tropical gose), Sundiver (Mexican lager), and Dungeon Map (West Coast IPA). Head to the online store (moderntimesmmerch.com) to put in your order, if you so desire.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 13, 2021. May be an image of drink and text that says 'GIGAZAPPER AZAPPER Times® EMPLOYEE Moder WEST BEER BEER WNED DIPA COAST'.

node.text: NOW AVAILABLE: Gigazapper. This 8% West-Coast style marvel of DIPA wizardry was built on a base of 2-row, Vienna malt, and white wheat before receiving a massive payload of Comet, Cashmere, El Dorado, and Amarillo Hops. Vibrant notes of grapefruit collide in the most delightful way imaginable with a profusion of pineapple, stone fruit, mango, and lemon/lime, creating a symphony of crisp, fruity refreshment that more than warrants its increased can size. You can snag these crimson beauts at our spots, as well as fine beer-slinging establishments where you normally see our stuff.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 13, 2021. May be an image of drink and text that says 'ACCOUNT SPECIALIST PHOENIX ORANGE COUNTY L.A. BAY AREA DENVER NOW HIRING Modern Times BEER'.

node.text:
NOW HIRING: Account Specialists. We are on the prowl for smooth-talking beer slingers to support our sales wizards and represent our fair brewery at festivals, tastings, and events all over the place. If you know beer, coffee, and how to facilitate a party, we'd love to hear from you. If you're located in any of the following areas, feel free to check out the full job description & apply via the link in our profile:
Phoenix, AZ
Orange County, CA
Los Angeles, CA 
Bay Area, CA 
Denver, CO

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 12, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text: NOW AVAILABLE: Cosmic Rays. This relentlessly tropical, unassailably-bomb 6.5% spectacle of hazecraft is the progeny of staggering quantities of Simcoe, Citra, Sabro, & Ekuanot hops. The convergence of these lupulin-laden marvels yields an abundance of tangerine, pineapple, coconut, & tropical fruit that enchants from aroma to lingering finish, leaving wistful memories in its wake. You can snag 4-packs at our spots, as well as fine beverage retailers throughout our regular disto-verse. For leads, feel free to hit up info@moderntimesbeer.com.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'CELEBRATING THE LIFE OF SATURDAY, Monsho JULY 3612 KURTZ ST SAN DIEGO SAVE THE DATE'.

node.text:
On 7/31, we'll be celebrating the life of Nate Soroko—a legend in the beer industry and a truly amazing human who we were incredibly fortunate to have in our lives. We'll be gathering with Nate's friends and family to reminisce, enjoy some fine beverages (both from MT and a bunch of guest breweries), and maybe even sing some Mariah Carey. 
—
This event will benefit a local San Diego non-profit that provides culinary apprenticeships to job seekers in need of a career and a fresh start.
